00:19:55,319 --> 00:19:56,320
Take a look.

271
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,400
A new rear wing.

272
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:07,979
You can see it as I am using

273
00:20:07,979 --> 00:20:10,960
the power of wind
to increase the car's lap speed.

274
00:20:11,559 --> 00:20:14,120
Each Formula A team has its unique technology.

275
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:15,280
Junda has brakes.

276
00:20:15,280 --> 00:20:17,240
Takano has high-performance power units.

277
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:19,680
Our past performances weren't satisfactory

278
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:20,920
largely because

279
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:23,240
we didn't have our unique technology.

280
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:26,680
So I thought I'd do some upgrades
on the Aerodynamics kit.

281
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:30,920
The problem with traditional wings
is that they are fixed

282
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:34,240
so their aerodynamic characteristics
cannot be changed.

283
00:20:34,759 --> 00:20:36,580
Either they have a large angle
and are fast in the turns,

284
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:38,419
or they have a small angle
and are fast in the straight track.

285
00:20:38,419 --> 00:20:39,860
We can only choose one of the two.

286
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:42,740
But if we have suitable materials
and an appropriate design,

287
00:20:42,740 --> 00:20:44,119
we can create a rear wing

288
00:20:44,119 --> 00:20:46,260
that becomes deformed by wind direction

289
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:48,079
at a speed of 250 kilometers per hour,

290
00:20:49,119 --> 00:20:50,840
guaranteeing the downforce in turns

291
00:20:50,840 --> 00:20:53,440
while the speed in the straight track
can further increase.

292
00:20:54,799 --> 00:20:57,600
So how much can my tail speed increase?

293
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,240
Theoretically,

294
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:03,540
the maximum speed will be
270 kilometers per hour.

295
00:21:03,540 --> 00:21:05,640
- That's a lot!
- 270?!

296
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,480
This isn't…

297
00:21:08,359 --> 00:21:09,880
four words.

298
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,000
Keep pressing and winning.

299
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,064
It's more like…

300
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,860
- Here.
- Turning the corner and winning.

301
00:21:14,860 --> 00:21:16,119
Yes.

302
00:21:16,119 --> 00:21:17,400
Impressive.

303
00:21:20,839 --> 00:21:21,856
However,

304
00:21:22,599 --> 00:21:23,759
if the wind conditions are inappropriate,

305
00:21:24,519 --> 00:21:26,400
airflow separation may occur
on the surface of the Aerodynamics kit,

306
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:28,599
making the vehicle out of control
due to loss of downforce

307
00:21:29,359 --> 00:21:31,920
or making the driver lose control of the car.

308
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:36,000
So the driver must cooperate very closely

309
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,480
with the engineer.

310
00:21:39,839 --> 00:21:42,319
You decide the best time to use it in the race.

311
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,064
That's right.

312
00:21:44,896 --> 00:21:45,984
Chen Mobai.

313
00:21:46,559 --> 00:21:49,344
Can you achieve the cooperation I mentioned?

314
00:21:52,736 --> 00:21:53,740
I can.

315
00:21:53,740 --> 00:21:54,920
Of course, he can!

316
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:56,939
Right?

317
00:21:56,939 --> 00:21:58,920
Although I didn't understand much,
I'm very impressed

318
00:22:01,119 --> 00:22:03,200
Ok, Xu Gong, it's up to you now.

319
00:22:03,759 --> 00:22:04,780
Leave it to me.

320
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:05,920
Let's go.

321
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:08,256
Be careful. Easy with it.

322
00:22:08,256 --> 00:22:09,839
Let's go to technical training.

323
00:22:29,359 --> 00:22:30,659
Chen Mobai came in second.

324
00:22:30,659 --> 00:22:32,920
He did quite well in this qualifying race,

325
00:22:33,759 --> 00:22:36,680
but that Mitsui is so good at corners.

326
00:22:37,319 --> 00:22:38,400
He still took pole position from him.

327
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:41,239
You even know what pole position means now,

328
00:22:41,239 --> 00:22:42,400
getting all professional.

329
00:22:43,559 --> 00:22:45,359
Thanks to your good teaching, Senior.

330
00:22:47,759 --> 00:22:49,359
They ran to the finish line of the race,

331
00:22:50,119 --> 00:22:51,640
but you ran into my heart.

332
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:56,839
Will we be able to see Chen Mobai in a bit?

333
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,640
I guess so.

334
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,440
We can go catch him later.

335
00:23:31,279 --> 00:23:32,320
Skipping meals

336
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,560
and hiding here,

337
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:42,680
what a workaholic.

338
00:23:43,599 --> 00:23:44,839
You don't have to do these things.

339
00:23:46,279 --> 00:23:48,400
I want to personally clean
the car you're racing in.

340
00:23:51,839 --> 00:23:52,864
What's the story?

341
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:56,800
Will an engineer cleaning a car
produce a champion?

342
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:00,199
I'm being nice to it

343
00:24:00,199 --> 00:24:02,079
because I want it to take you home safely.

344
00:24:19,079 --> 00:24:20,128
Shen Xi.

345
00:24:21,839 --> 00:24:22,880
After I win this race,

346
00:24:25,039 --> 00:24:26,048
I have something to say to you.

347
00:24:34,359 --> 00:24:35,559
I also have things to tell you.

348
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:40,720
But for today's race,

349
00:24:42,039 --> 00:24:43,072
don't think about anything else.

350
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:46,119
Just focus on the game,

351
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,808
okay?

352
00:24:53,759 --> 00:24:54,848
I promise.

353
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:06,976
Chen Mobai. Chen Mobai.

354
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,000
Hello.

355
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,360
I'm seeing the real person.

356
00:25:14,360 --> 00:25:15,520
Hi. Hello. Hello.

357
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:16,576
Nice to meet you.

358
00:25:17,279 --> 00:25:18,759
Okay.

359
00:25:18,759 --> 00:25:19,808
Hi.

360
00:25:20,799 --> 00:25:22,319
My name is Wang Duobao.

361
00:25:22,319 --> 00:25:23,559
I wanted to sponsor you before

362
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:25,279
but you rejected me.

363
00:25:25,839 --> 00:25:26,839
I'm the boss of a tractor factory.

364
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,008
Remember?

365
00:25:31,552 --> 00:25:32,579
I'm your fan.

366
00:25:32,579 --> 00:25:33,664
I've liked you for a long time.

367
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:35,400
Can you take a photo with me?

368
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,640
Sure.

369
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:39,080
Thank you. Look, look at this.

370
00:25:39,080 --> 00:25:40,319
I prepared it for you.

371
00:25:40,319 --> 00:25:41,792
[Go Chen Mobai]
Here, can you hold it?

372
00:25:42,359 --> 00:25:45,079
Okay. Three, two, one. Cheese.

373
00:25:46,599 --> 00:25:47,599
Thank you so much.

374
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,248
Thank you.

375
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:51,712
Miss Engineer.

376
00:25:52,359 --> 00:25:53,408
Miss.

377
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:55,880
You two should take a photo.

378
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:57,799
Come on, I'll take one for you.

379
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:00,640
Let's take one.

380
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:01,728
Come on.

381
00:26:02,319 --> 00:26:03,440
Here we go.

382
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,599
Three, two.

383
00:26:05,559 --> 00:26:06,560
What are you doing?

384
00:26:07,319 --> 00:26:08,319
You look awkward.

385
00:26:09,279 --> 00:26:10,336
Right?

386
00:26:19,119 --> 00:26:20,279
That's right. Here we go.

387
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:23,279
Come on. Three, two, one.

388
00:26:27,488 --> 00:26:28,559
That's great. It was nice.

389
00:26:28,559 --> 00:26:29,559
I'll send it to Manager Hao later.

390
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:31,559
- I'll leave now.
- Okay.

391
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:33,472
Good luck!

392
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:37,599
[Go Chen Mobai]
Duobao tractors, made in China.

393
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,160
Good luck.

394
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:46,279
Right, Miss, he likes you.

395
00:27:05,359 --> 00:27:06,368
Anyway…

396
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:08,512
There's still some time.

397
00:27:09,599 --> 00:27:12,940
You might want to go back
to the lounge and get some rest.

398
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:16,064
Okay, then.

399
00:27:18,119 --> 00:27:19,168
See you in the afternoon.

400
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,728
See you in the afternoon.

401
00:28:02,759 --> 00:28:03,776
Do you have some time to talk?

402
00:28:12,839 --> 00:28:14,519
I'm not one to beat around the bush.

403
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:16,416
Just cut to the chase.

404
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,000
I want to make things clear

405
00:28:20,559 --> 00:28:21,664
about why I came to Takano and Junda.

406
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:25,984
It's because of you.

407
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:28,512
I want to see how capable you are

408
00:28:29,599 --> 00:28:31,119
and whether you're good enough for her.

409
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,119
You're quite frank,

410
00:28:43,359 --> 00:28:44,416
but thank you anyway.

411
00:28:45,039 --> 00:28:46,519
My relationship with Shen Xi
is none of your business.

412
00:28:47,559 --> 00:28:48,640
I don't mean to interfere.

413
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:53,640
I just hope you can understand who Xi is.

414
00:28:58,119 --> 00:28:59,168
You might know

415
00:29:00,440 --> 00:29:03,160
Shen Xi is a double Ph.D.
in mechanical engineering and fluidics

416
00:29:04,279 --> 00:29:05,312
but

417
00:29:06,119 --> 00:29:08,240
you don't understand that someone like her

418
00:29:08,880 --> 00:29:10,119
only appears once in decades.

419
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:13,984
When she was in school,

420
00:29:14,519 --> 00:29:15,616
she led the team

421
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:19,160
and won the world championship
of the College Student Formula.

422
00:29:21,319 --> 00:29:22,319
Then she joined Markus

423
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:27,008
and became the only Chinese

424
00:29:27,920 --> 00:29:29,079
female engineer on the super race track.

425
00:29:30,119 --> 00:29:31,240
Do you know what that means?

426
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:36,319
It means she's excellent.

427
00:29:39,319 --> 00:29:40,400
Since the excellent her chose me,

428
00:29:42,440 --> 00:29:43,520
I'm not so bad either.

429
00:29:49,039 --> 00:29:50,112
I like your confidence

430
00:29:51,519 --> 00:29:52,608
and I appreciate your abilities.

431
00:29:53,599 --> 00:29:55,160
But even for someone like Shen Chuan,

432
00:29:56,279 --> 00:29:57,344
it took a long time

433
00:29:58,279 --> 00:29:59,296
to enter the Super Grand Prix.

434
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:01,024
How about you?

435
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,552
How long do you need?

436
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:08,359
Do you want Xi to wait for you on the spot?

437
00:30:12,559 --> 00:30:13,680
She is a fish that belongs in the sea,

438
00:30:14,559 --> 00:30:15,759
and you shouldn't let her

439
00:30:16,359 --> 00:30:19,168
stay in the pond for you.

440
00:30:25,279 --> 00:30:26,519
Your dream will surely come true.

441
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:29,720
Our dream will also come true.

442
00:30:31,808 --> 00:30:32,864
I always believe

443
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,839
that as long as we are together,

444
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,039
there are no hurdles we can't overcome.

445
00:30:38,319 --> 00:30:40,279
There is no end we can't reach.

446
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,264
It's been this way,

447
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:45,824
and it always will be.

448
00:30:52,559 --> 00:30:54,000
How do you know I am not that sea?

449
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,080
Lin Shaoqian.

450
00:30:59,519 --> 00:31:00,608
You said

451
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,839
that a racer needs to let
his engine do the talking.

452
00:31:05,759 --> 00:31:06,784
And today,

453
00:31:08,319 --> 00:31:09,559
I will let you listen well

454
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:13,119
to the engine that belongs to me.

455
00:31:35,039 --> 00:31:36,860
Cheng, I don't understand why

456
00:31:36,860 --> 00:31:38,340
Weishi continues to invest

457
00:31:38,340 --> 00:31:40,780
when the Ruifeng Group's financial statements

458
00:31:40,780 --> 00:31:43,159
are already so bad. Have you forgotten

459
00:31:43,159 --> 00:31:45,000
about the agreement between us?

460
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:49,279
Let me tell you something. If you lose,
you have to bear the money.

461
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:52,200
Of course, I haven't forgotten.

462
00:31:52,799 --> 00:31:56,640
In this meeting, we just want
to explain to you face to face.

463
00:31:57,200 --> 00:32:00,519
I don't think that any
explanation can satisfy me.

464
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,008
Please.

465
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:12,680
Are you sure you want to do this?

466
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:14,000
I thought we agreed to take a gamble.

467
00:32:18,016 --> 00:32:19,072
Hello, everyone.

468
00:32:19,599 --> 00:32:23,240
Today we will not only make an explanation
to Yellow Stone,

469
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:25,400
but we also make an invitation.

470
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:28,059
We hope Yellow Stone can join Weishi

471
00:32:28,059 --> 00:32:29,359
in co-investing Ruifeng.

472
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:36,000
Zhao, I've always liked your sense of humor.

473
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:39,200
But remember, in a hard time,

474
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:41,559
any jokes cannot make the situation better.

475
00:32:42,599 --> 00:32:44,480
Why don't you watch a race with us first?

476
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:48,620
The Formula A Championship in Linhai Stop

477
00:32:48,620 --> 00:32:50,039
is about to start.

478
00:32:50,799 --> 00:32:52,059
We can see that the audience

479
00:32:52,059 --> 00:32:53,520
is taking their seats one after another.

480
00:32:53,520 --> 00:32:56,700
Various teams have begun
their preparations in full swing.

481
00:32:56,700 --> 00:32:59,040
Watch the game? Are you kidding me?

482
00:32:59,559 --> 00:33:01,360
We have only one day. It's today.

483
00:33:01,360 --> 00:33:02,880
Tomorrow morning, we need to leave.

484
00:33:03,839 --> 00:33:07,104
So why do we need to waste
our time to watch the game?

485
00:33:07,104 --> 00:33:08,192
Tell me.

486
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:10,160
Mr. Grasso,

487
00:33:10,160 --> 00:33:12,440
you have attended so many business meetings.

488
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:15,780
You know that those beautiful words

489
00:33:15,780 --> 00:33:17,480
and fancy presentations

490
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:19,380
are really a waste of time.

491
00:33:19,380 --> 00:33:20,704
That's right.

492
00:33:20,704 --> 00:33:23,199
Mr. Grasso, don't you want to know

493
00:33:23,199 --> 00:33:25,119
what makes them still trust Ruifeng

494
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:28,799
and what is the bottom line
that we dare to propose

495
00:33:28,799 --> 00:33:29,888
co-investment?

496
00:33:30,720 --> 00:33:31,744
I promise.

497
00:33:32,359 --> 00:33:33,799
We just need half an hour.

498
00:33:33,799 --> 00:33:36,680
You will have a satisfactory answer.

499
00:33:38,519 --> 00:33:39,584
Mr. Grasso,

500
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:41,599
we Chinese say,

501
00:33:42,279 --> 00:33:44,559
as we come, so be it.

502
00:33:45,359 --> 00:33:46,519
Let's just take a look.

503
00:33:52,799 --> 00:33:53,824
You have a big nerve.

504
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:56,440
Mobai has to win the championship today

505
00:33:58,119 --> 00:33:59,440
to satisfy him.

506
00:34:00,519 --> 00:34:01,799
Since we decided to take a gamble,

507
00:34:02,559 --> 00:34:03,640
let's go all in.

508
00:34:05,319 --> 00:34:06,940
If he can't win the championship,

509
00:34:06,940 --> 00:34:07,960
Maituo won't live long anyway.

510
00:34:09,159 --> 00:34:11,199
I hope we can have a great victory.

511
00:34:13,519 --> 00:34:15,199
Working with you needs a strong heart.

512
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:22,079
Did you rearrange the car
based on the data given yesterday?

513
00:34:22,599 --> 00:34:23,616
Yes, it's all set.

514
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,740
The track temperature is quite high today.

515
00:34:30,740 --> 00:34:32,920
- Remember to check the tire pressure.
- Okay.

516
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:35,000
Make sure all the sensors are working properly.

517
00:34:53,199 --> 00:34:55,424
Keep an eye on the weather radar,
and prepare for a wet race.

518
00:35:00,079 --> 00:35:01,536
Wang, is this all set?

519
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:04,599
Ready to race, all the numbers match.

520
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,392
Hello?

521
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:53,824
Junda.

522
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:57,179
There are five minutes left for the countdown.

523
00:35:57,179 --> 00:35:58,659
Most of the race cars

524
00:35:58,659 --> 00:36:00,800
have completed their checks and adjustments.

525
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:02,320
They've reached the starting line.

526
00:36:21,239 --> 00:36:22,760
Why isn't Mobai here yet?
There are only five minutes left.

527
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,760
Xu Gong, Monkey, go look for him.

528
00:36:32,096 --> 00:36:33,119
Chen Mobai.

529
00:36:33,119 --> 00:36:34,304
Mobai.

530
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,096
What took you so long?

531
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,880
Chen Mobai.

532
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:43,440
No matter what happened,

533
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:45,599
stay calm now.

534
00:36:55,719 --> 00:36:56,800
Don't worry.

535
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:01,120
Wait for me.

536
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:48,579
Starting from the pole position,

537
00:37:48,579 --> 00:37:51,260
Mitsui Taku is very calm at this moment.

538
00:37:51,260 --> 00:37:54,379
the "King of Asian Racing" seems
to have won on the starting line

539
00:37:54,379 --> 00:37:56,719
and ready to continue dominating the track.

540
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:59,740
We can see trailing behind him

541
00:37:59,740 --> 00:38:00,880
to start the race

542
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:04,719
is Chen Mobai who stumbled
in the first two rounds.

543
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:08,040
From my observation,
he's looking quite good today.

544
00:38:08,040 --> 00:38:11,520
After Shen Chuan, no Chinese person
